title: Cafe At Arcosanti
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Buffet, Salad bar, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers a continental breakfast, lunch buffet, and dinner buffet or a la carte, with vegan choices. Has Wi-Fi, and a beer/wine bar is available at dinner. Stunning architecture and views of high desert landscape. Interstate 17, exit 263.
